                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ringkasan",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4912,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_4293187669096717509.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Набу Маликата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Nabu Malikata telah menciptakan Khvarena, yang berubah menjadi burung surgawi, Simurgh.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4910,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/59da6a8cbcffa112e5d2b63788d7051e_1480677671668697202.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Руккхадевата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Greater Lord mengubah Khvarena menjadi Simurgh agar dapat menjaga hutan. Para Pari, yang lahir dari Simurgh, adalah pendamping Rukkhadevata. Ketika informasi tentang Greater Lord dihapus dari",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7087,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Irminsul",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", Pari sekarang diperlakukan sebagai pendamping yang akrab dengan",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 2850,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/29/35428890/f29490bddc56b4a6773b6c5003bbb853_9091170755650648414.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Nahida",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4780,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/a5b8d23dd3fbe0969cc3ebce78f9c29f_8021351765588020911.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Эгерия",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Setelah kematian Egeria, dia menjadi danau Amrita yang murni. Simurgh meminum Amrita dan menghancurkannya menjadi potongan-potongan kecil. Dari kepingan-kepingan ini, lahirlah Pari.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Simurgh",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Seekor burung surgawi, yang dari tubuhnya lahirlah Pari.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7033,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/29/237301566/960461c3413ef1a52a3d848543f4ef41_3476359838263448819.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Аранары",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Teman pendampingnya Archon Dendro.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5744,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/07/237301566/6a703b5594dddc959dd10d08702bcbe1_383537773634930376.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Дайнслейф",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Selama Cataclysm, Dainsleif bertempur bersama dengan Pari pertama, Zurvan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Saudara Pengembara",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Selama Cataclysm, Saudara bertempur bersama dengan Pari pertama, Zurvan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Orde Pembenaran",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Anggota Orde Pembenaran menipu Pari untuk mendapatkan Lagu Agung Khvarena.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 20,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/16/70239714/f00d18b57acb4aa37bf2fc39bf67ddd0_830350480334963652.gif",
